# AI-Powered Customer Support Ticket System

## Project Overview

This project uses NLP and Machine Learning techniques to analyze customer support tickets.

## Features

* Ticket Classification
* Priority Prediction
* Customer Segmentation using KMeans
* NLP Text Processing
* Power BI Dashboard Visualization
* FastAPI Deployment

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Scikit-learn
* FastAPI
* Power BI
* NLP
* Hugging Face

